Operation Text:
INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

UPDATE bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
SET ESTATUS_CRU= 'FINALIZADO',
FECHA_CRU=  FROM_UNIXTIME( UNIX_TIMESTAMP(), 'dd/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss' )
WHERE TABLA_CRU=UCASE('KTON4BT')
SELECT * FROM bddlalm.ext_egresos_ingresos where periodo_contable = 201807  and cta_contable = '5401' AND tipo_egreso_final IN ('RECLASIFICACIONES')

--query reporte de Egresos a la tabla SELECT tipo_egreso_final, COUNT (cdsinies) as NO_PAGOS, SUM (im_neto_egreso) as IMPORTE  FROM bddlalm.ext_egresos_ingresos    where periodo_contable = 201807  and cta_contable = '5401'    GROUP BY tipo_egreso_final    order by tipo_egreso_final

-- query reporte de Ingresos a la tabla  SELECT tipo_ingreso, COUNT (cve_siniestro) as NO_PAGOS, SUM (mto_neto) as IMPORTE  FROM bddlapr.opr_egresos_ingresos    where periodo_contable =201807 and tipo_ingreso <> 'NULL'    GROUP BY tipo_ingreso    order by tipo_ingreso

-- query reporte de Ingresos a la tabla  SELECT tipo_ingreso, COUNT (cve_siniestro) as NO_PAGOS, SUM (mto_neto) as IMPORTE  FROM bddlapr.opr_egresos_ingresos    where periodo_contable =201807 and tipo_ingreso <> 'NULL'    GROUP BY tipo_ingreso    order by tipo_ingreso

SELECT tipo_egreso_final, COUNT (cdsinies) as NO_PAGOS, SUM (im_neto_egreso) as IMPORTE  FROM bddlalm.ext_egresos_ingresos    where periodo_contable = 201807  and cta_contable = '5401'    GROUP BY tipo_egreso_final    order by tipo_egreso_final

select count(*) from(                             select                                  a.CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CDMCT, CDMCR, NUMOVIMI,                                 cast(concat(substr(cast (feoperac as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (feoperac as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (feoperac as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as feoperac_fch,                                  TCTIPMOV, TCCDMONE, string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (feoperac as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as feoperac_fch,                                  TCTIPMOV, TCCDMONE, IMESTIMA, IMSALVAD, IMPORSAL,  IMMOVIMI, INREISAL, INFACSAL, NUMOVECO, 'h' AS INDORI, sistorig                             from bddlcru.ksim61h a                             INNER JOIN ( ---/* <== 20180920 AUT_ConsDef_CC006.- Se agrega inner join hacia KSIM10 */                                 SELECT DISTINCT                                     s.CDSINIES                                 FROM (                                         SELECT                          on (a.CDSINIES=c.CDSINIES)                             where trim(a.cdsinies) <>'')o

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero, cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero, b.cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero2,                 case when a.cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero = b.cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero as cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta,cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero                         )A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero  as cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero IS NOT NULL) AND cve_categoria_vehiculo_tercero2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

select count(*) 
from bddltrn.cob_completas_emision z 
left join bddldes.preparacion_emi_cob a  
    on  z.num_poliza    =a.num_poliza 
    and z.num_version=a.num_version                              -- 367803145
left join bddldes.insumos_autos_p13_union aa  
    on z.num_poliza=aa.num_poliza 
    and z.num_version=aa.num_version 
    and  z.cve_cobertura_tarificable=aa.cve_cobertura_tarificable --367803307
left join bddldes.contrato_coaseguro_040919 aaa 
    on z.num_poliza=aaa.num_poliza                                -- 367803307
left join 
(
    select a.cve_contrato_coaseguro,a.cve_compania_coaseguradora,
           b.desc_compania_coaseguradora
      from bddldes.aut_companias_coaseguradora a

             on a.cve_compania_coaseguradora = B.cve_compania_coaseguradora 
     where  B.cve_compania_coaseguradora is not null

               SELECT -- tipo de afectado contrario   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCPOASCO,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSPOASCO                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITACG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) d             on (a.TCPOASCO=d.TCPOASCO)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de persona juridica   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCPEFIJU,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSPEFIJU                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KPETCAG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) e             on (a.TCPEFIJU=e.TCPEFIJU)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de via   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tctipvia,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dstipvia                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTCTTVG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) f             on (a.tctipvia=f.tctipvia)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de comunicacion ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tcticom1,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dsticom1                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITACG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) g             on (a.tcticom1=g.tcticom1)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de pvehiculo   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tctipveh,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dstipveh                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT2OG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) h             on (a.tctipveh=h.tctipveh)             left outer join              (                 SELECT --uso del vehiculo   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS cdusoveh,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dsusoveh                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT2SG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) i             on (a.cdusoveh=i.cdusoveh)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- armadora   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCARMADO,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSARMADO                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT3KG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) j             on (a.TCARMADO=j.TCARMADO)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de persona juridica   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tcpefprp,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dspefprp                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KPETCAG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) m             on (a.tcpefprp=m.tcpefprp)

coalesce(DSPEROBJ     ,'') as DSPEROBJ,                 NUPOIREL,                  INPORES,                  DSOBJPOI,                  CDSECDOM,                  INFRAUDE_calc,                  INCULPA_calc,                  feterper_fch,                  fealtper_fch,                 a.TCSITEAP,                  coalesce(dssiteap     ,'') as dssiteap,                 a.TCPOASCO,                  coalesce(DSPOASCO     ,'') as DSPOASCO,                 a.TCPEFIJU,                  coalesce(DSPEFIJU     ,'') as DSPEFIJU,                 CDFILCCO,                  NUREFCCO,                  CDOBJTP,                 CTNUOCO,                  a.CDUSOVEH,                  coalesce(dsusoveh     ,'') as dsusoveh,                 NUMATVCO,                  INPALCOC,                  INCONPOL,                  INDASALA,                  CDICEACO,                  DSCOLVCO,                  INCOLDIR,                  a.TCTIPVIA, coalesce(dstipvia     ,'') as dstipvia,                 NODIROBJ,                  NUDIROBJ,                  TCCOPOST,                  NOPOBOBJ,                  DSCONCC,                  a.TCTICOM1,                  coalesce(dsticom1     ,'') as dsticom1,                 TCPREPA1,                  NUTELF1,                  NUEXTEL1,                  fenacco1_fch,                  fepecon1_fch,                  TCSEXO,                  DSCONTAC,                 a.TCARMADO,                  coalesce(DSARMADO     ,'') as DSARMADO,                  a.TCCARROC, 				coalesce(desc_carroceria     ,'') as desc_carroceria,  --- <--- 20191107 IMEDRANO : Esta es la posicion que debe ocupar en la tabla fisica productiva                 CDVERVEH,                  DSVEHICU,                  VAVEHIC,                  INPTACT,                  INDEROB,                  feinirob_fch,                 a.TCTIPVEH,                  coalesce(dstipveh     ,'') as dstipveh,                 VAMODELO,                 DSNUMSER,                  DSNUMMOT,                  DSRFV,                  CDFILPRP,                  CDIDFPRP,                  DNAP1PRP,                  DNAP2PRP,                  DNNOMPRP,                 a.TCPEFPRP,                  coalesce(dspefprp     ,'') as dspefprp,                TCTIDPRP,                 NUPRECL1,                 TSULTMOD,                 sistorig             from (  ---                      select distinct                         ---- tabla 1                          u1.CDSINIES, u1.CTNUPOIN, CDFILIAC, CDCONVEN, TCPEROBJ, /*INPERNOI, TCTIPOBJ,*/ NUPOIREL, INPORES, DSOBJPOI, CDSECDOM,                          case                              when trim(INFRAUDE) in ('N','0') then 'N'                              when trim(INFRAUDE) in ('S','1') then 'S'                              else INFRAUDE                         end as INFRAUDE_calc,                          case                              when trim(INCULPA) in ('N','0') then 'N'                              when trim(INCULPA) in ('S','1') then 'S'                              else INCULPA                        end as INCULPA_calc,                          /*INTIPANT, TCSITPER, */                         cast(concat(substr(cast (feterper as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (feterper as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (feterper as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as feterper_fch,                         cast(concat(substr(cast (fealtper as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fealtper as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fealtper as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as fealtper_fch,                         TCSITEAP,                          TCPOASCO,                          TCPEFIJU,                          CDFILCCO, NUREFCCO, CDOBJTP,                          ---- tabla 2                         CTNUOCO, CDUSOVEH, trim(NUMATVCO) as NUMATVCO, INPALCOC, INCONPOL, INDASALA, CDICEACO, DSCOLVCO, /*INCICOS,*/ INCOLDIR,                          TCTIPVIA, trim(NODIROBJ) as NODIROBJ, NUDIROBJ, TCCOPOST, trim(NOPOBOBJ) as NOPOBOBJ, trim(DSCONCC) as DSCONCC, TCTICOM1, TCPREPA1, NUTELF1, NUEXTEL1,                          cast(concat(substr(cast (fenacco1 as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fenacco1 as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fenacco1 as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as fenacco1_fch,                         cast(concat(substr(cast (fepecon1 as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fepecon1 as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fepecon1 as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as fepecon1_fch,                         TCSEXO, trim(DSCONTAC) as DSCONTAC, TCARMADO, TCCARROC, CDVERVEH, trim(DSVEHICU) as DSVEHICU, VAVEHIC, INPTACT, INDEROB,                         concat(trim(TCTIPVEH),trim(TCARMADO),trim(TCCARROC)) as cve_tac_vehiculo,                         cast(concat(substr(cast (feinirob as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (feinirob as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (feinirob as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as feinirob_fch,                         TCTIPVEH, VAMODELO,  trim(DSNUMSER) as DSNUMSER, trim(DSNUMMOT) as DSNUMMOT, trim(DSRFV) as DSRFV, CDFILPRP, trim(CDIDFPRP) as CDIDFPRP,                         trim(DNAP1PRP) as DNAP1PRP, trim(DNAP2PRP) as DNAP2PRP, trim(DNNOMPRP) as DNNOMPRP, TCPEFPRP, TCTIDPRP, NUPRECL1, TSULTMOD,                         'INFO' as sistorig                     from (                             select distinct                                 a.CDSINIES, a.CTNUPOIN, a.CDFILIAC, a.CDCONVEN, TCPEROBJ, /*INPERNOI, TCTIPOBJ,*/                                  NUPOIREL, INPORES, DSOBJPOI, CDSECDOM, INFRAUDE, INCULPA, /*a.INTIPANT, TCSITPER,*/                                  FETERPER, FEALTPER, TCSITEAP, TCPOASCO, TCPEFIJU, CDFILCCO, NUREFCCO, a.CDOBJTP, TSULTMOD                             from (                                          select                                               CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CDFILIAC, CDCONVEN, TCPEROBJ, /*INPERNOI, TCTIPOBJ,*/                                              NUPOIREL, INPORES, DSOBJPOI, CDSECDOM, INFRAUDE, INCULPA,  /*INTIPANT, TCSITPER,*/                                              FETERPER, FEALTPER, TCSITEAP, TCPOASCO, TCPEFIJU, CDFILCCO, NUREFCCO, CDOBJTP, TSULTMOD                                          from bddlcru.ksim20t                                           where cdsinies = '0098314834'                                       union all                                          select                                               CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CDFILIAC, CDCONVEN, TCPEROBJ, /*INPERNOI, TCTIPOBJ,*/                                              NUPOIREL, INPORES, DSOBJPOI, CDSECDOM, INFRAUDE, INCULPA,  /*INTIPANT, TCSITPER,*/                                              FETERPER, FEALTPER, TCSITEAP, TCPOASCO, TCPEFIJU, CDFILCCO, NUREFCCO, CDOBJTP, TSULTMOD                                          from bddlcru.ksim20h                                           where cdsinies = '0098314834'                             ) a                             inner join (select distinct CDSINIES                                         from (                                                     select CDSINIES                                                    from bddlcru.ksim10t                                                  where tctipsin = 'AU'                                                   -- and cdsinies = '0089346035'                                             union                                                  select  CDSINIES                                                    from bddlcru.ksim10h                                                  where tctipsin = 'AU'                                                    --and cdsinies = '0089346035'                                           ) s                              ) b                              on (b.CDSINIES = a.CDSINIES)                         ) u1                     left outer join (                                                  select distinct                                 CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CTNUOCO, CDUSOVEH, NUMATVCO, INPALCOC, INCONPOL, INDASALA, CDICEACO, DSCOLVCO, /*INCICOS,*/ INCOLDIR,                                  TCTIPVIA, NODIROBJ, NUDIROBJ, TCCOPOST, NOPOBOBJ, DSCONCC, TCTICOM1, TCPREPA1, NUTELF1, NUEXTEL1, FENACCO1, FEPECON1,                                  TCSEXO, DSCONTAC, TCARMADO, TCCARROC, CDVERVEH, DSVEHICU, VAVEHIC, INPTACT, INDEROB, FEINIROB, TCTIPVEH, VAMODELO,                                  DSNUMSER, DSNUMMOT, DSRFV, CDFILPRP, CDIDFPRP, DNAP1PRP, DNAP2PRP, DNNOMPRP, TCPEFPRP, TCTIDPRP, NUPRECL1                             from (                                                              select                                              CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CTNUOCO, CDUSOVEH, NUMATVCO, INPALCOC, INCONPOL, INDASALA, CDICEACO, DSCOLVCO, /*INCICOS,*/ INCOLDIR,                                              TCTIPVIA, NODIROBJ, NUDIROBJ, TCCOPOST, NOPOBOBJ, DSCONCC, TCTICOM1, TCPREPA1, NUTELF1, NUEXTEL1, FENACCO1, FEPECON1,                                              TCSEXO, DSCONTAC, TCARMADO, TCCARROC, CDVERVEH, DSVEHICU, VAVEHIC, INPTACT, INDEROB, FEINIROB, TCTIPVEH, VAMODELO,                                              DSNUMSER, DSNUMMOT, DSRFV, CDFILPRP, CDIDFPRP, DNAP1PRP, DNAP2PRP, DNNOMPRP, TCPEFPRP, TCTIDPRP, NUPRECL1                                         from bddlcru.ksia24t a                                           -- where cdsinies = '0089346035' and CTNUPOIN = 7                                  union                                         select                                              CDSINIES, CTNUPOIN, CTNUOCO, CDUSOVEH, NUMATVCO, INPALCOC, INCONPOL, INDASALA, CDICEACO, DSCOLVCO, /*INCICOS,*/ INCOLDIR,                                              TCTIPVIA, NODIROBJ, NUDIROBJ, TCCOPOST, NOPOBOBJ, DSCONCC, TCTICOM1, TCPREPA1, NUTELF1, NUEXTEL1, FENACCO1, FEPECON1,                                              TCSEXO, DSCONTAC, TCARMADO, TCCARROC, CDVERVEH, DSVEHICU, VAVEHIC, INPTACT, INDEROB, FEINIROB, TCTIPVEH, VAMODELO,                                              DSNUMSER, DSNUMMOT, DSRFV, CDFILPRP, CDIDFPRP, DNAP1PRP, DNAP2PRP, DNNOMPRP, TCPEFPRP, TCTIDPRP, NUPRECL1                                         from bddlcru.ksia24h a                                           -- where cdsinies = '0089346035' and CTNUPOIN = 7                                 ) a                         ) u2                     on ( u1.CDSINIES=u2.CDSINIES and u1.CTNUPOIN=u2.CTNUPOIN)              ) a             --nuevo jc             left outer join (                 select                     TCTIPVEH as cve_tipo_vehiculo,                     CDARMAD  as clave_armadora,                     CDCARRO  as cve_carroceria,                     DSCARRO  as desc_carroceria                 from  bddlcru.KTPT2IT ) as z                 on z.cve_tipo_vehiculo=a.tctipveh AND                    z.clave_armadora=a.tcarmado AND                    z.cve_carroceria=a.tccarroc                              left outer join              (                 SELECT --tipo de afectado   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCPEROBJ,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSPEROBJ                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITTIG' AND trim(CDEMPRES) = '0001' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) b             on (a.TCPEROBJ=b.TCPEROBJ)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- situacion tecnica de apertura   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tcsiteap,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dssiteap                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITSTG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) c             on (a.tcsiteap=c.tcsiteap)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de afectado contrario   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCPOASCO,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSPOASCO                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITACG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) d             on (a.TCPOASCO=d.TCPOASCO)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de persona juridica   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCPEFIJU,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSPEFIJU                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KPETCAG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) e             on (a.TCPEFIJU=e.TCPEFIJU)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de via   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tctipvia,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dstipvia                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTCTTVG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) f             on (a.tctipvia=f.tctipvia)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de comunicacion ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tcticom1,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dsticom1                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KSITACG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) g             on (a.tcticom1=g.tcticom1)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de pvehiculo   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tctipveh,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dstipveh                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT2OG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) h             on (a.tctipveh=h.tctipveh)             left outer join              (                 SELECT --uso del vehiculo   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS cdusoveh,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dsusoveh                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT2SG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) i             on (a.cdusoveh=i.cdusoveh)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- armadora   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS TCARMADO,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as DSARMADO                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KTPT3KG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) j             on (a.TCARMADO=j.TCARMADO)             left outer join              (                 SELECT -- tipo de persona juridica   ---ok                     TRIM(CDELEMEN) AS tcpefprp,                     trim(DSELEMEN) as dspefprp                     FROM  BDDLCRU.KTCTGET                 WHERE TRIM(CDTABLA)='KPETCAG' AND CDIDIOMA ='ES'             ) m             on (a.tcpefprp=m.tcpefprp)

select ---- tabla 1 tcpefprp                 CDSINIES,                  CTNUPOIN,                  CDFILIAC,                  CDCONVEN,                 a.TCPEROBJ,                  coalesce(DSPEROBJ     ,'') as DSPEROBJ,                 NUPOIREL,                  INPORES,                  DSOBJPOI,                  CDSECDOM,                  INFRAUDE_calc,                  INCULPA_calc,                  feterper_fch,                  fealtper_fch,                 a.TCSITEAP,                  coalesce(dssiteap     ,'') as dssiteap,                 a.TCPOASCO,                  coalesce(DSPOASCO     ,'') as DSPOASCO,                 a.TCPEFIJU,                  coalesce(DSPEFIJU     ,'') as DSPEFIJU,                 CDFILCCO,                  NUREFCCO,      INCONPOL,                  INDASALA,                  CDICEACO,                  DSCOLVCO,                  INCOLDIR,                  a.TCTIPVIA, coalesce(dstipvia     ,'') as dstipvia,    ,'') as dsticom1,                 TCPREPA1,                  NUTELF1,                  NUEXTEL1,                  fenacco1_fch,                  fepecon1_fch,                  TCSEXO,                  INDEROB,                  feinirob_fch,                 a.TCTIPVEH,                  coalesce(dstipveh     ,'') as dstipveh,                 VAMODELO,                 DSNUMSER,                  DSNUMMOT,                  DSRFV,                  CDFILPRP,                  CDIDFPRP,                  DNAP1PRP,                  DNAP2PRP,                  DNNOMPRP,    /*INTIPANT, TCSITPER, */                         cast(concat(substr(cast (feterper as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (feterper as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (feterper as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as feterper_fch,                         cast(concat(substr(cast (fealtper as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fealtper as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fealtper as string),7,2)) as as string),1,4),'-',substr(cast (fepecon1 as string),5,2),'-',substr(cast (fepecon1 as string),7,2)) as timestamp) as fepecon1_fch,                         TCSEXO, trim(DSCONTAC) as DSCONTAC, select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio, ban_litigio2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.ban_litigio, b.ban_litigio2,                 case when a.ban_litigio = b.ban_litigio2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio as ban_litigio                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta,ban_litigio                         )A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio  as ban_litigio2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (ban_litigio IS NOT NULL) AND ban_litigio2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio, ban_litigio2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.ban_litigio, b.ban_litigio2,                 case when a.ban_litigio = b.ban_litigio2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio as ban_litigio                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta,ban_litigio                         )A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio  as ban_litigio2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, ban_litigio                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (ban_litigio IS NOT NULL) AND ban_litigio2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT    DISTINCT    PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado,    PERFIL.num_poliza,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_inicial,    PERFIL.fch_vigencia_final,      SEG.segmento,        INTEGRALIDAD.pol_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.pol_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.poliza_total,        INTEGRALIDAD.prima_autos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_danos,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_salud,    INTEGRALIDAD.prima_vida,        INTEGRALIDAD.ramos        FROM       (SELECT        DISTINCT        num_poliza,        id_participante_consolidado,        fch_vigencia_inicial,        fch_vigencia_final                FROM bddldes.crm_01_tablero_perfil_oct19        WHERE cve_ramo = "AU"        AND cve_rol in ('TOM','PAG') ) AS PERFIL    LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        segmento                            FROM bddldes.crm_segmento_tom_oct19) AS SEG    ON SEG.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado        LEFT JOIN    (SELECT        DISTINCT        id_participante_consolidado,        pol_vida,        pol_danos,        pol_salud,        pol_autos,        poliza_total,        prima_vida,        prima_danos,        prima_salud,        prima_autos,        ramos                FROM bddldes.crm_02_tablero_integralidad_oct19        WHERE tipo_integralidad = "RAMOS" --AND    ) AS INTEGRALIDAD    ON INTEGRALIDAD.id_participante_consolidado = PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado     ORDER BY PERFIL.id_participante_consolidado )OJPO ORDER BY 1,2

Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta,  b.num_afectado,                  case when a.cve_armadora_tercero = b.clave_armadora2 then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_armadora_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.desc_armadora_tercero = b.desc_armadora2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_desc_armadora_tercero,                  case when a.cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero = b.cve_uso_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero = b.desc_uso_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.num_serie_vehiculo_tercero = b.num_serie_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_num_serie_vehiculo                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_armadora_tercero,                         desc_armadora_tercero,                         cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         num_serie_vehiculo_tercero                         from   bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R' and year(fch_contable) = 2019                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_armadora_tercero, desc_armadora_tercero, cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero, desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         num_serie_vehiculo_tercero) A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, num_afectado,                         MAX(clave_armadora)  as clave_armadora2,                         MAX(descr_armadora)  as desc_armadora2,                         MAX(cve_uso_vehiculo) as cve_uso_vehiculo2,                         MAX(descr_uso_vehiculo) as desc_uso_vehiculo2,                         MAX(num_serie)  as num_serie_vehiculo2                         from bddlalm.aut_siniestro_afectado                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, num_afectado, clave_armadora, descr_armadora, cve_uso_vehiculo, descr_uso_vehiculo, num_serie )B                 on                         trim(a.cve_siniestro)  =   trim(b.cve_siniestro) and                         a.num_afectado =   b.num_afectado

case when a.cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero = b.cve_uso_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero = b.desc_uso_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.num_serie_vehiculo_tercero = b.num_serie_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_num_serie_vehiculo                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_armadora_tercero,                         desc_armadora_tercero,                         cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         num_serie_vehiculo_tercero                         from   bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R' and year(fch_contable) = 2019                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_armadora_tercero, desc_armadora_tercero, cve_uso_vehiculo_tercero, desc_uso_vehiculo_tercero,                         num_serie_vehiculo_tercero) A                 inner join                         (select     from bddlalm.aut_siniestro_afectado                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, num_afectado, clave_armadora, descr_armadora, cve_uso_vehiculo, descr_uso_vehiculo, num_serie )B val_cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero, cve_carroceria_tercero, cve_carroceria2, val_cve_carroceria_tercero, desc_carroceria_tercero, desc_carroceria2, val_des_carroceria_tercero,                   desc_vehiculo_tercero, desc_vehiculo2, val_desc_vehiculo_tercero from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta,  b.num_afectado, a.cve_marca_vehiculo_tercero,                  b.marca_vehiculo_tercero2, a.cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero, b.modelo_vehiculo_tercero2, a.cve_carroceria_tercero, b.cve_carroceria2,                 a.desc_carroceria_tercero, b.desc_carroceria2, a.desc_vehiculo_tercero, b.desc_vehiculo2,                 case when a.cve_marca_vehiculo_tercero = b.marca_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_marca_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when a.cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero = b.modelo_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero,                 case when trim(a.cve_carroceria_tercero) = trim(b.cve_carroceria2)  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_cve_carroceria_tercero,                  case when a.desc_carroceria_tercero = b.desc_carroceria2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_des_carroceria_tercero,                 case when a.desc_vehiculo_tercero = b.desc_vehiculo2  then 'V'                 else 'F' end as val_desc_vehiculo_tercero                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_marca_vehiculo_tercero,                         cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero,                         cve_carroceria_tercero,                         desc_carroceria_tercero,                         desc_vehiculo_tercero                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R' and year(fch_contable) = 2019                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, num_afectado,                         cve_marca_vehiculo_tercero, cve_modelo_vehiculo_tercero, cve_carroceria_tercero,                         desc_carroceria_tercero, desc_vehiculo_tercero) A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, num_afectado, INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, b.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2,                 case when a.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero = b.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta)A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero IS NOT NULL) AND desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, b.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2,                 case when a.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero = b.desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta)A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero IS NOT NULL) AND desc_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero, b.cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2,                 case when a.cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero = b.cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta)A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero)  as cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero IS NOT NULL) AND cve_tipo_vehiculo_tercero2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

SELECT num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_endoso, *  from test_migracion.incidencia17  where num_poliza = '35451973' and  num_poliza_cobranza = '35450541'

create table bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura_base as
select
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
des_cobertura_contratada  ,
NVL(cve_asegurado,'') AS cve_asegurado,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,
mto_comision_derecho_poliza ,
mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),'')
))
idmd5  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL(cast(anio_mes_contable  as string),''),
fch_contable ,
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(cast(num_version_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza ,''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(des_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(cve_asegurado ,''),
NVL(identificador_nvo_renovado ,''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable ,''),
NVL(forma_pago   ,''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_prima_neta    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_derecho_poliza    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado     as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_isr_comisiones     as string),''),
NVL(cast( mto_importe_comision_total     as string),''),
NVL(cve_Identificador_intermediario,''),
NVL(des_Identificador_intermediario,''),
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
NVL(cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,''),
NVL(cast(porcentaje_comision    as string),''),
NVL(cve_sistema,'')
))
idmd5completo  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from (
SELECT
distinct
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,

cve_asegurado ,

cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,

mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_DLT AS
SELECT
CASE WHEN anio_mes_contable=0 THEN 140001 ELSE anio_mes_contable END AS anio_mes_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_contable IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_contable END AS fch_contable,
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
num_poliza_cobranza,
num_endoso,
forma_pago,
cve_tipo_endoso,
mto_prima_tecnica,
mto_recargo_descuento,
mto_prima_neta,
mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
pct_pago_prima,
mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
mto_derecho_poliza,
mto_cesion_comision,
mto_iva_poliza,
mto_prima_total,
cve_cobertura_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_emision IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_emision END AS fch_emision,
NVL(segmento, '') AS segmento,
NVL(desc_segmento, '') AS desc_segmento,
NVL(negocio, '') AS negocio,
NVL(desc_negocio, '') AS desc_negocio,
NVL(bonos, '') AS bonos,
NVL(desc_bonos, '') AS desc_bonos,
NVL(plan_incentivos, '') AS plan_incentivos,
NVL(pol_contr, '') AS pol_contr,
NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') AS desc_pol_contr,
NVL(contrb, '') AS contrb,
NVL(pol_prest, '') AS pol_prest,
NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') AS desc_pol_prest,
NVL(mot_exc, '') AS mot_exc,
NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') AS desc_mot_exc,
cve_canal_venta_alterno,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''))) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(forma_pago,'') ,NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_tecnica AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_descuento AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_cesion_comision AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(pct_pago_prima AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_derecho_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_iva_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_total AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT),0) AS STRING))) as idmd5completo,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS FECHAAUD,
cve_sistema_int
FROM(
select * from  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_DLT
) AS STG_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA
ORDER BY fch_contable,num_poliza,num_version_poliza, cve_sistema_int

select "", CVE_SISTEMA, "", "", FCH_CONTABLE, "", "", TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM, "", "", MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL, "" FROM ( SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'INFO' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 UNION ALL SELECT CVE_SISTEMA ,CAST(FCH_CONTABLE AS CHAR(10)) AS FCH_CONTABLE ,CAST(TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM AS DECIMAL(34,4)) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ,CAST(SUM(MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL) AS DECIMAL(34,3)) AS MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM (SELECT CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,AVG(TIPO_CAMBIO) OVER (PARTITION BY FCH_CONTABLE) AS TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM,MTO_IMPORTE_SINIESTRAL FROM BDDLALM.ALM_SOLICITUD_PAGO WHERE BAN_CONTABLE = 1 AND CVE_SISTEMA = 'RCLA' AND FCH_CONTABLE <= DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(),1) ) T GROUP BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE,TIPO_CAMBIO_PROM ORDER BY CVE_SISTEMA,FCH_CONTABLE DESC LIMIT 5 ) AS D

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_INFO_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA as
SELECT
CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable ,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_contable,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,7,2)," 00:00:00") AS timestamp) as fch_contable ,
CAST (num_poliza as varchar(14)) as num_poliza ,
CAST (indicador_vigencia as int) as vigencia_poliza,
CAST (num_version_poliza as int) as num_version_poliza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(8)) as num_poliza_cobranza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(6)) as num_endoso  ,
CAST (forma_pago as String) as forma_pago,
CAST ('' as varchar(3)) as cve_tipo_endoso,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_tecnica) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_tecnica,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_descuento) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_descuento,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta)AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_prima_neta,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado)AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
CAST (pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) as pct_pago_prima ,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
CAST (SUM(mto_derecho_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_cesion_comision) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_cesion_comision,
CAST (SUM(mto_iva_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_iva_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_total) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_total,
CAST(SUBSTR (cve_cobertura_contable,2,3) as varchar(3)) as cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_emision,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,7,2)) AS timestamp) as fch_emision,
CAST(segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS segmento,
CAST(desc_segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_segmento,
CAST(negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS negocio,
CAST(desc_negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_negocio,
CAST(bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS bonos,
CAST(desc_bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_bonos,
CAST(plan_incentivos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS plan_incentivos,
CAST(pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_contr,
CAST(desc_pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_contr,
CAST(contrb AS VARCHAR(300)) AS contrb,
CAST(pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_prest,
CAST(desc_pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_prest,
CAST(mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS mot_exc,
CAST(desc_mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_mot_exc,
'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER  as importe
group by num_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
anio_mes_contable,
cve_cobertura_contable,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
indicador_vigencia,
fecha_contable,
forma_pago,
fecha_emision,
pct_pago_prima
ORDER BY  fch_contable,cve_sistema_int,num_poliza,num_version_poliza

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER as
SELECT
substr(CAST(FECONTAB AS string),1,6) as anio_mes_contable,
CAST(FECONTAB as String) as fecha_contable,
CDNUMPOL as num_poliza,
CTVRSPOL as num_version_poliza,
INANCACO as indicador_vigencia,
CDMCT as cobertura_contable,
CDOBJTP as objeto_codigo,
CTSECOBJ as objeto_secuencia,
TCFORPAG as forma_pago,
SIGNO * PRTECNICA as mto_prima_tecnica,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRTECNICA)   as mto_recargo_descuento,
SIGNO * PRNETA  as mto_prima_neta,
SIGNO * (IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
PORCNFP as pct_pago_prima,
SIGNO * PRNETANFP as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CASE WHEN PORCNFP > 0 THEN SIGNO * (PRNETA  - PRNETANFP) else (SIGNO * PRNETA)  END as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
SIGNO * IMDERPOL as mto_derecho_poliza,
-1 * SIGNO * PRCEDIDA as mto_cesion_comision,
SIGNO * (IMIVA + GAIVA )as mto_iva_poliza,
SIGNO * (PRNETA - PRCEDIDA +IMREFRAC1 + IMREFRAC2 + IMDERPOL + IMIVA + GAIVA) as mto_prima_total,
CDRAMDGS as cve_cobertura_contable,
nvl(segmento,'') as segmento,
nvl(desc_segmento,'') as desc_segmento,
nvl(negocio,'') as negocio,
nvl(desc_negocio,'') as desc_negocio,
nvl(bonos,'') as bonos,
nvl(desc_bonos,'') as desc_bonos,
nvl(plan_incentivos,'') as plan_incentivos,
nvl(pol_contr,'') as pol_contr,
nvl(desc_pol_contr,'') as desc_pol_contr,
nvl(contrb,0) as contrb,
nvl(pol_prest,'') as pol_prest,
nvl(desc_pol_prest,'') as desc_pol_prest,
nvl(mot_exc,'') as mot_exc,
nvl(desc_mot_exc,'') as desc_mot_exc,
CAST(FEMISION as String) AS fecha_emision
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER  as ktom41t
order by fecha_contable, num_poliza,num_version_poliza

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_KTOM41T_FILTER AS
SELECT
ktom41t.CDNUMPOL,
ktom41t.CTVRSPOL,
ktom41t.CDRAMDGS,
kcim06t.INANCACO,
catalogo.DSFORPAG as TCFORPAG,
ktom41t.cdmct,
ktom41t.cdobjtp,
ktom41t.ctsecobj,
case when ktom41t.TCCOPERA= '003' then  -1 else  1 end as SIGNO,
ktom41t.impcec01 as PRTECNICA ,
ktom41t.impcec02 as PRCEDIDA,
ktom41t.impcec03 as IMREFRAC1,
ktom41t.impcec04 as IMDERPOL,
ktom41t.impcec05 as IMIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec06 as GAIVA ,
ktom41t.impcec07 as IMREFRAC2,
ktom41t.Impcec19 as PRNETA ,
ktom41t.impcec20 as PRTOTAL ,
KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 as PORCNFP,
(IMPCEC19 * (KCIM16T.IMCAAP15 / 100)) AS  PRNETANFP,

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo           actual
INNER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlalm.alm_recibo actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_delta
SELECT
CAST(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'') AS VARCHAR(10))				AS  cve_folio_agente_1,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_2,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(10))                                       	AS  cve_folio_agente_3,
CAST(NVL(RTRIM(cat.cve_canal_cobro), '') AS VARCHAR(20))		AS 	cve_canal_cobro,
CAST(NVL(ban.cdbanco,'') 			AS VARCHAR( 4))				AS  cve_banco,
CAST(NVL(mc.cve_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR( 3))				AS	cve_medio_cobro,
CAST(NVL(mc.descr_medio_cobro,'') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS 	descr_medio_cobro,
pol.cve_cobertura_contable                                      AS  cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo_anterior, '') AS VARCHAR(13))    AS  cve_estado_recibo_anterior,
cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_estado_recibo, '') AS varchar(1))				AS  cve_estado_recibo,
cat.descr_estado_recibo,
CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)                                         AS  fch_cambio_estado,
rec.fch_emision,
rec.fch_inicio_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(
NVL(CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00'), '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_movimiento,
CAST(
NVL(CASE
WHEN rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'   AND fch_p.fch_pago > 0
THEN
CONCAT(SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING), 1,4), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 5,2), '-',
SUBSTR(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago    AS STRING), 7,2),
' 00:00:00')
ELSE NULL
END, '1400-01-01 00:00:00.000')
AS TIMESTAMP)                                               AS  fch_pago,
rec.fch_fin_vigencia_recibo,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR( 1))				AS  cve_forma_pago,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago, '') 	AS VARCHAR(30))				AS  descr_forma_pago,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_recargo,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_comision_derecho_poliza,
CAST(0 AS DECIMAL(13,2))                                        AS  mto_descuento_volumen,
CAST(imp.iva        AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_iva,
CAST(imp.recargos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_recargo,
CAST(imp.derechos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST(imp.prima_neta AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_prima_neta,
rec.mto_total_pago,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision, '')   	AS 	VARCHAR( 1))  	AS	cve_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS	descr_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR( 1)) 	AS	cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(6))                                        AS  num_endoso,
rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza,
rec.num_poliza,
rec.num_recibo,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(8))                                        AS  num_poliza_cobranza,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_1,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_2,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_3,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_prima_total,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion, '') 	 AS	VARCHAR( 2))		AS	cve_tipo_transaccion,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion, '') AS	VARCHAR(40)) 		AS	descr_tipo_transaccion,
rec.num_version_poliza,
rec.vigencia_poliza,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema,
CAST(NULL   AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema_int,
CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP)              AS  fechaaud,
rec.ori_registro,
rec.fechaaud_registro,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex', CAST(rec.num_recibo AS STRING)) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
CONCAT(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'')
, NVL(cat.cve_canal_cobro,''), NVL(ban.CDBANCO,''), NVL(cve_medio_cobro,''), NVL(descr_medio_cobro,''), cve_cobertura_contable
, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')
, NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion,''), NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion,''), rec.num_version_poliza, rec.vigencia_poliza
))                                                      AS idmd5completo
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON
rec.num_poliza          = pol.num_poliza
AND rec.num_version_poliza  = pol.num_version_poliza
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_importe imp ON
rec.num_recibo = imp.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50 AS n50  ON
rec.num_recibo = n50.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro mc ON
rec.num_recibo = mc.num_recibo
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
rec.num_recibo          = ban.num_recibo
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_fch_pago fch_p ON
rec.num_recibo = fch_p.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_catalogos cat ON
rec.num_recibo = cat.num_recibo

CAST(imp.derechos   AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST(imp.prima_neta AS DECIMAL(15,3))                           AS  mto_prima_neta,
rec.mto_total_pago,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision, '')   	AS 	VARCHAR( 1))  	AS	cve_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS	descr_ind_nivel_emision,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') 	AS 	VARCHAR( 1)) 	AS	cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento, '') AS 	VARCHAR(15)) 	AS descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(6))                                        AS  num_endoso,
rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza,
rec.num_poliza,
rec.num_recibo,
CAST(''   AS VARCHAR(8))                                        AS  num_poliza_cobranza,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_comision,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_1,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_2,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  pct_participacion_agente_3,
CAST(NULL AS DECIMAL(15,3))                                     AS  mto_prima_total,
CAST(NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion, '') 	 AS	VARCHAR( 2))		AS	cve_tipo_transaccion,
CAST(NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion, '') AS	VARCHAR(40)) 		AS	descr_tipo_transaccion,
rec.num_version_poliza,
rec.vigencia_poliza,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema,
CAST(NULL   AS VARCHAR( 4))                                     AS  cve_sistema_int,
CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP)              AS  fechaaud,
rec.ori_registro,
rec.fechaaud_registro,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex', CAST(rec.num_recibo AS STRING)) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
CONCAT(NVL(pol.cve_folio_agente_1,'')
, NVL(cat.cve_canal_cobro,''), NVL(ban.CDBANCO,''), NVL(cve_medio_cobro,''), NVL(descr_medio_cobro,''), cve_cobertura_contable
, NVL(cve_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo_anterior,''), NVL(cve_estado_recibo,''), NVL(cat.descr_estado_recibo,'')
, NVL(CAST(n50.fch_movimiento AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(fch_p.fch_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_forma_pago,''), NVL(cat.descr_forma_pago,'')
, NVL(CAST(imp.iva AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.recargos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.derechos AS STRING),''), NVL(CAST(imp.prima_neta AS STRING),'')
, NVL(CAST(rec.mto_total_pago AS STRING),''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.descr_ind_nivel_emision,''), NVL(rec.cve_ind_tipo_movimiento,'')
, NVL(rec.descr_ind_tipo_movimiento,''), NVL(CAST(rec.num_fraccion_pago_poliza AS STRING),''), rec.num_poliza, NVL(rec.num_recibo,'')
, NVL(rec.cve_tipo_transaccion,''), NVL(cat.descr_tipo_transaccion,''), rec.num_version_poliza, rec.vigencia_poliza
))                                                      AS idmd5completo
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_poliza pol ON
rec.num_poliza          = pol.num_poliza
AND rec.num_version_poliza  = pol.num_version_poliza
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_importe imp ON
rec.num_recibo = imp.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50 AS n50  ON
rec.num_recibo = n50.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro mc ON
rec.num_recibo = mc.num_recibo
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban ON
rec.num_recibo          = ban.num_recibo
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_fch_pago fch_p ON
rec.num_recibo = fch_p.num_recibo
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_catalogos cat ON
rec.num_recibo = cat.num_recibo

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_n50
SELECT cdnumrec, MAX(fecmvto), MAX(fecontab)
FROM bddlcru.krbn50t n50
INNER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info ra ON
n50.cdnumrec = ra.num_recibo
WHERE n50.cdciagru = 'SA'
GROUP BY n50.cdnumrec

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro1
SELECT CAST(trim(t1.cdrefele) AS VARCHAR(12)), t1.numoveco, t1.nucobpar, t1.imremeco
FROM bddlcru.ktoa13t t1
INNER JOIN (
SELECT cdrefele, MAX(TSULTMOD) MAX_TSULTMOD
FROM bddlcru.ktoa13t a1
INNER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec ON
rec.num_recibo  =   trim(a1.cdrefele)
WHERE   a1.CDTIPELE =	'RB'
AND a1.CDCIAGRU =   'SA'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
GROUP BY cdrefele
) T2 ON
t1.cdrefele =   t2.cdrefele
AND t1.TSULTMOD =   T2.MAX_TSULTMOD
WHERE
t1.CDTIPELE =	'RB'
AND t1.CDCIAGRU =   'SA'
